## Verification
1. 訪問 http://localhost:3000 確認前端正常顯示
2. POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
   ```json
   {"username": "admin", "password": "admin123"}
   ```
3. 預期返回：`{"code": 200, "data": {"token": "..."}}`

